1. Core Management (CRUD)
Base URL: /api/students/management/
Endpoints:
GET /: List students with filters (Search, Class, Section).
POST /: Bulk-create student profiles (handles nested Personal, Guardian, and Additional info).
GET /{id}/: Retrieve deep-nested profile details.
PUT/PATCH /{id}/: Update specific sections (e.g., updating only Emergency Contact).
DELETE /{id}/: Soft or hard delete student records.
2. Student 360-Degree Profile (Analytics)
Base URL: /api/students/profile/
Endpoints:
GET /{id}/: Master record view for the UI dashboard.
GET /{id}/academic_performance/: Returns GPA, Rank, and Improvement metrics.
GET /{id}/attendance_summary/: Aggregated attendance percentages.
GET /{id}/discipline_history/: Detailed log of behavioral incidents.